The critical split: `appsettings.json` uses `Host=postgres` (Docker DNS name), `appsettings.Development.json` uses `Host=localhost` (port-forwarded from Docker to your machine). When running `dotnet run` locally with `ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT=Development`, the development overrides apply automatically, so you connect to Docker via `localhost:5432`.

